Overview:
  loose coupling
  well defined, but complex
  reusable components
  hub/ router
  better than command
  decouple objects
  specific

examples:
  java util timer
  java lang reflect method

design:
  interface based
  concrete class
  minimizes inheritance
  mediator knows about colleagues
  mediator and concrete mediator

Pitfalls:
  deity object
  limits subclassing
  over or with command